text: Frederick Francis Dawson (19 June 1917 – 27 April 1986) was a New Zealand cricketer. Born in Timaru, Dawson played three first class matches for Canterbury in the 1950–51 season. He died, age 68, in Christchurch. == References == Category:1917 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Cricketers from Timaru Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Canterbury cricketers
